    "Html": "\r\n<p>First off: thanks for this great tool.</p>\r\n<p>Despite I have not seen the code thoroughly, just take a look at it, I have inspected the SMTP packets through WireShark and come to the conclusion that just two concurrent connections are allowed. I was wondering if there is an easy way to tweak that number.\r\n I think that would be a nice feature to include in the options form, as it would allow performance testing of Smtp clients.</p>\r\n<p>Vicente Almagro</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id=\"-chrome-auto-translate-plugin-dialog\" style=\"background-color:transparent!important; top:0px; left:0px; overflow-x:visible!important; overflow-y:visible!important; z-index:999999!important; text-align:left!important; padding:0px!important; margin:0px!important\">\r\n<div style=\"max-width:300px!important; color:#fafafa!important; border-color:#000000!important; border-width:0px!important; background-color:#363636!important; font-size:16px!important; padding:8px!important; overflow:visible!important; z-index:999999!important; text-align:left!important\">\r\n</div>\r\n<img src=\"http://www.google.com/uds/css/small-logo.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"z-index:-1!important; right:1px!important; top:-20px!important; padding-top:3px!important; padding-right:5px!important; padding-bottom:0px!important; padding-left:5px!important; margin:0px!important\"></div>\r\n",
